* Wolfgang Banzhaf, P. Nordin, R. Keller, F. Francone (1998): &quot;Genetic Programming - An Introduction&quot;, Morgan Kaufmann, San Francisco. 
* Kenneth A. de Jong (2006): &quot;Evolutionary Computation: A Unified Approach.&quot; MIT Press, Cambridge, MA. 
* Melanie Mitchell (1996): &quot;An Introduction to Genetic Algorithms.&quot; MIT Press, Cambridge MA. 
* Hans-Paul Schwefel (1995): &quot;Evolution and Optimum Seeking&quot;. Wiley &amp; Sons, New York. 

